## Dataset

- **Source:** [Online Retail II — UCI ML Repository](https://archive.ics.uci.edu/dataset/502/online+retail+ii) | [Kaggle Mirror](https://your-kaggle-link)
- 1M+ transactions from a UK-based online retailer (2009–2011)
- Key columns: `CustomerID`, `InvoiceNo`, `Quantity`, `UnitPrice`, `InvoiceDate`, `Country`

> Download the dataset and place it in `data/raw/` before running any notebooks.

